{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 170°C. Grease a springform cake tin (24 cm) with butter, then dust with a little flour and set aside.","Place chocolate into mixing bowl and grate <nobr>8 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl.","Add caster sugar, yoghurt, milk, eggs, vanilla bean paste and 100 g butter and mix <nobr>40 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Add potato flour, salt and 230 g plain flour and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>.","Add yeast and mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Transfer half of the cake batter into prepared tin. Lay pear slices on top of batter, then sprinkle with cocoa powder. Transfer remaining batter into tin over the top.","Bake for 40 minutes (170°C).If the cake is browning too quickly on the top, cover with aluminium foil and return to the oven and continue cooking for a further 15-20 minutes or until a wooden skewer inserted into the centre of the cake comes out clean. Leave cake to cool in tin, and then dust with icing sugar, slice and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g butter, cut into pieces, plus extra for greasing","230 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","150 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces","200 g caster sugar","120 g natural yoghurt","80 g full cream milk","3 eggs","1 tsp vanilla bean paste","70 g potato flour","1 pinch salt","2 tsp dried instant yeast","2 pears, (approx. 250 g), peeled and cut into  slices (1 cm)","2 tbsp cocoa powder","2 tbsp icing sugar, for dusting"]}],"id":"r98878","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-IAaYu8aaZEg\/XZWpyK-IoYI\/AAAAAAAAfPE\/7qCWSxAuqpMsAYaKCBNhtwZXmVs-xhlagCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_6Q35XzfWgfC79Tql.png","title":"Chocolate and pear cake","publishedAt":"2015-08-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.8 g","fat":"12.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"49 g","calories":"1393 kJ \/ 331 kcal"},"usefulItems":"springform cake tin (24 cm), wooden skewer, aluminium foil, oven","hintsAndTricks":["You can serve this cake warm if desired. Try drizzling over a warm caramel sauce for an extra decadent treat."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 30m","12 portion"]}